Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.06,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:35.76,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.42,0:24:04.46,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.55,0:25:34.60,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No! She can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.83,0:00:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.09,0:01:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dojima?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.31,0:01:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! Dojima's headed for Namatame's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.36,0:01:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Namatame's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, whadduya mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.11,0:01:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me! I need to speak to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dojima! Please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Nanako have to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me back Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dojima!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Give her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}D-Dojima?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Give her back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he still alive when Nanako's dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:01:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dojima!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forgive Namatame either!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Dojima!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She's... She's all I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dojima?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, get him to his room!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Dojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,kill him myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dojima...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he seriously gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,His only daughter's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing woulda surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,First he killed Konishi,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and now Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why is he the one who gets to go on living?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He tried to use the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You have your life, and now you want your freedom, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault that Nanako's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,12 o'clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Midnight Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I failed to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you got in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How? The real one's right here, and we already beat his Shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The law can't touch me, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this how you truly feel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To hell with the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't ever forgive what you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If the law can't touch you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,then we'll have to punish you ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Hanamura! What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You hate me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Living or dying makes no difference to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't dare, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll continue "saving" people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}It's my mission!{rockin' the 100ms fadeout, ohh yeah}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever we want, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!{r-ram it in}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be a luxury suite. Most hospital wards don't have such large televisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, with something like this in the room, this man could escape at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Although once he enters,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.27,0:04:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,he may find there's no way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just gonna turn your back and walk away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it! What's gotten into you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, that's not how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How very unbecoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.47,0:05:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If any of you want no part in this, just leave the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.02,0:05:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I just wanted to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So she wouldn't get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just gonna let him go, Yu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our only chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, the guy's gonna get off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he'll go around "saving" people again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to put an end to this ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That will make us no different than him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We must...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We must...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,reach out to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't {\i1}this{\i0} the truth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the reality right in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we're missing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Missing? Like what, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of this bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Yosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We should calm down and think rationally about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize now that we've heard almost nothing from Namatame's perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we possibly understand someone who says killing people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is the same as "saving" them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We all know how you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but we've accomplished this much together, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. So let's figure this out together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think as hard as I can and try to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go ahead and think this through as much as we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If we leave any unanswered questions behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd just be lying to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:07:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,there's something that's bothering me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he start killing people in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he said it was to "save" them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard's sick in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,After the first murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the police called in Namatame for questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But everything in his testimony and his bearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what they looked at, they found nothing suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he faked it real well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe he started out with a normal motive and got a taste for killing after the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If that were the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,his motive for killing the announcer would be even more inexplicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe his wife was getting suspicious, and she got in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Namatame and his wife were separated at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi already knew about Ms. Yamano beforehand,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and Namatame was shocked to hear of Ms. Yamano's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have no convincing motive for Namatame to kill Yamano Mayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}Although, her name {\i1}was{\i0} written in Namatame's own diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so confusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie, don't just stand there and say—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Teddie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use. He's not picking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he went home ahead of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably shouldn't call the house phone at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure he's there when I go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fog! Poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's poisonous fog!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's snowing.{tl note: yuki means snow.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yosuke,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.46,0:10:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,let us know when you find Teddie, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see ya tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to make snowmen with you when it snows!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah! Let's make a big one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In his room, was it right to stop everyone from what they were about to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I...{am crying like a bitch}{brotag losing his shit}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I was in the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing in such a lonely place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Now I remembear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the deal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to thinking last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If he "saves" people by killing them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't he actually have failed to save us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And another thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Namatame who appeared on the Midnight Channel
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,said that he failed to save Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe he really was trying to save the victims
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,by putting them inside the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But he still threw in Konishi and Ms. Yamano, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Or what,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you think someone else was involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The warning letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The warning letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I know what's been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the letters I received.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe the first one said,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't rescue anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The second said,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you don't stop this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,someone close will be put in and killed."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn't that kinda odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Would someone who thinks he's saving people by killing them write stuff like "don't rescue" or "kill"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and the "will be put in and killed" part doesn't make sense either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.47,0:13:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If the killer was writing it, wouldn't it be more like, "I'll put in and kill"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You think someone else wrote it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than the Kubo incident, we were all convinced there was only one culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In Namatame's parlance,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"failing" would've been the first two cases, when the victims died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:13:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Warning letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all come here to find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell us everything you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're willing to listen to my story?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the only ones who can fully understand what you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I returned to my parents' house, as if to run away from the scandal surrounding my affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Onto our next story...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}City council secretary Namatame Taro's affair with TV announcer Yamano Mayumi has been exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't been able to reach Mayumi at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(0,100)}For several days, the—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now for our next story...{shitty news anchors}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm sure you were expecting this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A corpse was found hanging from an antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}According to the preliminary police investigation and from her belongings and clothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}she has been identified as local TV announcer Ms. Yamano Mayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the Midnight Channel was just an urban legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that have been an SOS from Mayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:16:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So I desperately kept watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that girl from the liquor shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,After agonizing over it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to meet her
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and told her to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But...{daga... otoko da}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...she didn't take me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew she was gonna be murdered,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but I couldn't save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was mortifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when I made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I could hide her somewhere no one,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,not even the killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,could find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to tell me it's safe over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought, no matter what kind of place it might be,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's better than being slaughtered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Once things calmed down, I could just let her out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I explained the situation to the victims, they wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just take them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought my job as a deliveryman would be the perfect cover for my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I did call the police, but they didn't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was the only one who could help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When I went after that little girl and entered the TV myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I had doubts about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew you couldn't even get out of that place on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You really were trying to save people, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I secretly believed myself to be a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess from your point of view,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,people did stop dying once you started "saving" people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you did it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the more you really believed you were preventing their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... such a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't belong anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true? My eyes aren't playing tricks on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck yeah. Miracles {\i1}do{\i0} happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God! Oh, thank God!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, Teddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:20:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell is that dumb bear at an important time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Coming up,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}we have the weather forecast for Inaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The continual fog is beginning
Dialogue: 2,0:20:16.07,0:20:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}to strongly impact people's mental health.
Dialogue: 7,0:20:20.57,0:20:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We strongly urge the residents of Inaba to remain calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not be alarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You are fast asleep in the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we take a moment to look back on your journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that you have friends who are willing to follow the same path as you through this dense fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:21:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The bonds you share with your friends have blessed you with the Judgment Arcana.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I envy you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,for you have forged so many bonds in such a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Empress Arcana as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem we have a bond connecting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall confirm our direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The car will be parked here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be worth your while to take the time to stop and reflect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The case on Kubo Mitsuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.43,0:22:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.35,0:22:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But it isn't raining today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A gift... to celebrate your sister's recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.23,0:22:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.03,0:22:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked around all day and didn't hear anything good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.32,0:22:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,To find facts that even the police overlooked would be difficult indeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.66,0:22:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,now that over half a year has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I need some fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Naoto's stumped, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.72,0:22:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, Yu? Y-You what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!{lollll the bgm}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You ate it all?! And so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.85,0:22:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a difficult battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!{naisu}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,To clear my head after eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's freezing out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.50,0:23:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you go back in?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this'll get my deductive muscles flexing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.67,0:23:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Junes is invading! Everyone, run for it! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.05,0:23:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be someone in town...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who meets all of the criteria for this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The killer must have a connection to both Konishi and Ms. Yamano...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as be in a position to observe our actions periodically to some extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.36,0:23:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, it must be someone who could approach your house without arousing suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.28,0:23:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who meets all the criteria...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.39,0:25:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't he here when we need him?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.89,0:25:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.98,0:25:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea who that might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.02,0:25:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.56,0:25:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn in Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.36,0:25:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no running away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.90,0:25:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Let's go!
